msgstr "is confused about what he has known, but he lies in full awareness, saying that he has known and seen and heard and sensed, he commits an offense entailing confession when seven conditions are fulfilled:"

#. REF: pts-vp-en.2.170
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc1:2.6.14"
msgid "pubbevassa hoti “musā bhaṇissan”ti, bhaṇantassa hoti “musā bhaṇāmī”ti, bhaṇitassa hoti “musā mayā bhaṇitan”ti, vinidhāya diṭṭhiṃ, vinidhāya khantiṃ, vinidhāya ruciṃ, vinidhāya bhāvaṃ."
